      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Core Primitives:\n\nAgent(LLM Agent) - Receive input, Call LLM, Decides Action\nTool - A function which Agent can call to do beyond conversation\nSession - Chat History + task",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
