    {
      "id": "TJxqyqMnPrpfkzJJyXOL9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 163,
      "y": 1606,
      "width": 741.6795654296875,
      "height": 325,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aN",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1483636117,
      "version": 320,
      "versionNonce": 1422520571,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779508027455,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Session : One conversation thread -> That store message, tool calls,results\n\n State: Key value pair, that stores current conversation\n\nmemory : Spans across multiple session . Long term knowledge . Persistant \nacross session (database)\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Session : One conversation thread -> That store message, tool calls,results\n\n State: Key value pair, that stores current conversation\n\nmemory : Spans across multiple session . Long term knowledge . Persistant \nacross session (database)\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "WWuc3DO67yL4ShzmsoRvp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 98.8125,
      "y": 1838.546875,
      "width": 497.6328125,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 505425685,
      "version": 36,
      "versionNonce": 251335413,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779508068691,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Multi - Agent System:",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Multi - Agent System:",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "_fObk1SNkVGIIcmaPj4UY",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 86,
      "y": 1911,
      "width": 577.0996704101562,
      "height": 400,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aQ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 700084827,
      "version": 438,
      "versionNonce": 259452693,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779508226233,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "One agent: \n\n-> Long instruction and you have one LLM\n-> There is no specilization - agent behave like medicore\n-> It doens't work well with complex task\n\n\nMulti-agent System:\n-> Specilization -> one agent is specilised for task\n-> Hierarchy -> parent agent delgate task to sub agent\n-> Modularity -> Each agent won't look on other task task\n-> Parallel -> Two agents execute simuntaneously\n\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "One agent: \n\n-> Long instruction and you have one LLM\n-> There is no specilization - agent behave like medicore\n-> It doens't work well with complex task\n\n\nMulti-agent System:\n-> Specilization -> one agent is specilised for task\n-> Hierarchy -> parent agent delgate task to sub agent\n-> Modularity -> Each agent won't look on other task task\n-> Parallel -> Two agents execute simuntaneously\n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "LLrFyZT71k8cplIhv9anI",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 54,
      "y": 2253,
      "width": 842.5794067382812,
      "height": 300,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aR",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 357114843,
      "version": 435,
      "versionNonce": 1073548245,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779508374944,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "How Delegation works:\n\n1. sub_agent parameter in LLMagent\n2. parent agent will read subagent name and description\n3. when user query arrives, the parent agent decide which subagent to call\n4. Parent calls the chose sub_agent( tools)\n5. Subagent will process the query and completes the task and results back to Parent\n6. parent will synthesis the final output to user\n\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How Delegation works:\n\n1. sub_agent parameter in LLMagent\n2. parent agent will read subagent name and description\n3. when user query arrives, the parent agent decide which subagent to call\n4. Parent calls the chose sub_agent( tools)\n5. Subagent will process the query and completes the task and results back to Parent\n6. parent will synthesis the final output to user\n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "q4iGvxSJlgwumqFSLB5_1",
