      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779511176253,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. These are the custom python function that will be executed at specific point\nduring the agent execution by ADK\n\n2. Logging, Validation and gaurdrails - without modifying the agent itself",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. These are the custom python function that will be executed at specific point\nduring the agent execution by ADK\n\n2. Logging, Validation and gaurdrails - without modifying the agent itself",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "MrLcs6FFqHoNNlc1Kdg1g",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 58,
      "y": 3144,
      "width": 944.4393310546875,
      "height": 375,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ab",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1563648501,
      "version": 605,
      "versionNonce": 1365182395,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779511429288,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "before_agent_callback ->  Before Agent process it's input -> it checks the input, authentication\nafter_agent_callback -> After agent produces final output -> Format output, log the output\n\nbefore_tool_callback -> Before any tool is called -> rate limit, Tokens, Track cost, guardrails\nafter_tool_callback -> After tool call compelted -> Caching the result, error_handling\n\nbefore_model_callback -> Before LLm model get called -> System prompt augmentation\nafter_model_callback -> after llm model executed -> Hallucination check\n\n\n\n\n\n\n ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "before_agent_callback ->  Before Agent process it's input -> it checks the input, authentication\nafter_agent_callback -> After agent produces final output -> Format output, log the output\n\nbefore_tool_callback -> Before any tool is called -> rate limit, Tokens, Track cost, guardrails\nafter_tool_callback -> After tool call compelted -> Caching the result, error_handling\n\nbefore_model_callback -> Before LLm model get called -> System prompt augmentation\nafter_model_callback -> after llm model executed -> Hallucination check\n\n\n\n\n\n\n ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
